<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>404 - Page Not Found</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            height: 100vh;
        }

        .container {
            text-align: center;
        }

        h1 {
            font-size: 4rem;
            color: #333;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        p {
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            color: #666;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

        a {
            color: #007bff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        a:hover {
            text-decoration: underline;
        }

        .illustration {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 500px;
            margin-bottom: 30px;
        }

       
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <img src="404-error.png" alt="404 Illustration" class="illustration">
        <h1>404 - Page Not Found</h1>
        <p>Oops! The page you're looking for doesn't exist.</p>
        <p>Go back to <a href="/">homepage</a> or <a href="mailto:support@example.com">contact support</a> if you need assistance.</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
